Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,508)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  珊迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bonjour, Mademoiselle Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你带来了老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have brought your usual
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹堡套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one Krusty Kombo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过吃的就用不着你给了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I won't be needing the food
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.68,0:01:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己从老家带了点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought a little something of my own from home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从老家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪的熏烤坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's smokin' barbecue nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外带食品不得进入蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no outside food allowed at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不说出来  坚果秘密就不会暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't spill the nuts if you won't
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.21,0:01:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfecto
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.59,0:01:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来尝一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫做火辣德州
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call Texas heat
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过咱真得趁蟹老板没发现赶快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we really should stop before Mr. Krabs finds out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发现什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finds out what?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.57,0:02:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外带食品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outside food
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你网开一面  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mercy, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她不知道她那样是在犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She knows not the error of her ways
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.04,0:02:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你尝一口坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet one taste of these nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包你会改口的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll whistle a different tune
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要没收未经允许擅自带入的橡子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm confiscerating these unauthorized acorns
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这擅自带进来的坚果哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so good about these unauthorized nuts anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你被录用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, you're hired
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To do what?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然是在蟹堡王做坚果出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, to make those nuts at me restaurant, of course
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're delicirous
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是真觉得我会应聘这工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a few pickles shy of a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you think I'm looking for a job
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  这可不单单是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, this is no mere job
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是使命召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a calling
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是应尽的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a duty to serve
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是成真的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a dream come true
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.90,0:03:04.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干就干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:04.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我需要个烧烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll need me a barbecue grill
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个海军老妙计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an old Navy trick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以临时做烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for makeshift barbecues
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不算太破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not too shabby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒是可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon she'll do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把珊迪调教好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure to show her the ropes, boy-o
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(818,806)}每日特餐  烤坚果
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barbecue nuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人倒是什么都能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These customers will eat anything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回味无穷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice aftertaste
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪和海绵宝宝在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's in the kitchen with SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们两个都在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're in the kitchen, we two
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪和海绵宝宝在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's in the kitchen with SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架上面烤坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Makin' nuts on the barbecue
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见蟹老板说的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard the boss man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说说要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's what
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神奇的魔法就在这里展现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this here is where the magic happens
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要能尊重这个神圣的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as the sacred space is respected
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.57,0:03:55.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整间厨房都能一团和气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:55.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the kitchen will remain in perfect harmony
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to worry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在这就像一根绳上的蚂蚱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be like two crickets on a fiddle in here--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把自己敲晕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock yourselves out, please
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经在烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Already on it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说我要烤多少坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So how many nuts should I fix up?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.17,0:04:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There must be a mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是蟹黄堡的单子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are all for Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来宣传坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get the word out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.26,0:04:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该挺想来吃点美味新品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon you're hankering for a delicious new dish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挺不想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Certainly not
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每天都买一模一样的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I procure the same patty every day
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我有精炼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I have a refined--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好有烟熏味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such smoky sapidity
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.76,0:04:38.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:38.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪的熏烤坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's smokin' barbecue nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好吃  对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty good, am I right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不仅仅很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not just pretty good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好到可以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but good enough to go on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the big screen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,768)}来尝尝珊迪的熏烤坚果\N超神    满分
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来尝尝珊迪的熏烤坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Try Sandy's smokin' barbecue nuts"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear that, everyone?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位的屁股也爱坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's butt loves those nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来点坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take some nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的屁股从来不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His butt's never wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want some
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.12,0:05:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.08,0:05:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doggy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we're cookin'
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果需求大增
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Demand for nuts is up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以得增加供应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we're increasing supply
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让开  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, gee, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可能会害可怜的珊迪累垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you might be overwhelming poor Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烧烤午餐高峰期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's the barbecue lunch rush
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.40,0:06:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是有人想吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody wants a Krabby Patty, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now giddyup
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有餐点都上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the orders are up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.97,0:06:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有餐点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那份是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.03,0:07:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会再摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more wobble
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢新装修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you love the new look?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是来这吃坚果的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just here for the nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.49,0:07:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛仔王坚果小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kowboy Krab's Nut Shack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1638,424)}牛仔王\N坚果小屋
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯子才全来这吃坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's full of nuts, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能不能把钳子递过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hand me them tongs over there, will ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在实在是忙得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm busier than a six-legged horse in tap shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must breathe
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果自有黄金屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's gold in them there nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,袋子里有什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in the bags, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这袋是下一轮烤坚果的点餐单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's the next round of barbecue nut orders
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你帮我我帮你  互惠互利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, scratch my back and call me a cactus
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那袋装的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what about that one?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.14,0:08:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装的都是没用的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's full of useless Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经是没人要了  全变垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody really wants 'em, so they're garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在烤我面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just toasting my buns
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让开  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move over, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你挡我倒垃圾的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're blocking me trash
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱钱钱钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money, money, money
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果坚果坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuts, nuts, nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱不会自己烤自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That money won't barbecue itself
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱钱的清香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love the smell of money
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烟味比平常重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little smokier than usual
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  拖什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, what's the holdup?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问问你的烧烤大厨好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask your pitmaster?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她不烤坚果了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She stopped barbecuing nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.81,0:09:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陆地生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Land dweller
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm plumb out of nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用光什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're plumb out of what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉了  牛仔王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kowboy Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你赚钱只能另寻他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you have to find another way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make your dough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚果树已经干枯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The nut tree's done run dry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想买到珊迪的熏烤坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't reckon we can get
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no Sandy's smokin' barbecue nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能没有珊迪是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without no Sandy, can we?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.24,0:10:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Riot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这桌子沾上了德州烟熏味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This table's got that smoky Texas tang
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太迷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪坚果的烟味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The smoke from Sandy's nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把蟹堡王的东西都腌入味了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has flavored everything in this restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chow time
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.12,0:10:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, that smells delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是没用的陈年蟹黄堡罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a useless old Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有木刺的美食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snack without splinters
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How novel
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该可以分点蟹黄堡吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we could partake in your patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want some of those
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Orders up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good news
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾堡现在涨价一倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trashy Patties are now double the price
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些蟹黄堡应该是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon these patties are on the house
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来大家今天都为坚果狂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we all went a little nuts today
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是回味无穷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still a nice aftertaste
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.59,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs150\fsp45\bord4\shad6}海胆哥与败蜗子
