Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动动脚来坐坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move your feet and grab your seat
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.58,0:12:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆哥与败蜗子秀  开播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:12:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "The Sir Urchin and Snail Fail Show"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开播了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.42,0:12:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.06,0:12:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112,244)}海胆哥与败蜗子秀
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是  海胆哥与败蜗子秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "The Sir Urchin and Snail Fail Show"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woe is me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得来人给我的无价艺术珍品掸个灰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My priceless works of art need to be dusted
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,败蜗子过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Snail Fail
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir Urchin, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给艺术品掸个灰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dust my art
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  海胆哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very good, Sir Urchin, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.38,0:12:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掸的出神入化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You dust divinely
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给背面也掸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now dust the back
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵遵遵命  海胆哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,V-v-very good, Sir Urchin, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高雅高雅高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dainty, dainty, dainty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的确可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why you, indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为何我们大家不可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not any of us?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倘若宇宙的本质就是随机性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the nature of the universe is random
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为何厄运就不愿平等降临在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would not misfortune find us all equally?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而现今确乎如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And yet, it does not
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你应该不再发问  你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should stop asking, "Why you?"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而开始问  我为何可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and start asking, "Why me?"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是台词
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not the line
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不打我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop hitting me?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想让观众明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want the audience to know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个真正的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I am a real thespian
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不单单是在台上装疯卖傻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and not just some bumbling buffoon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想认认真真当演员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you wanna be a serious actor?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人拦你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody's stopping you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上下台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exit stage left
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,754)}请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没开玩笑  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no joke, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们最爱的喜剧组合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our favorite comedy team
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直播一半就解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just broke up on live TV
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.85,0:14:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动动脚来坐坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move your feet and grab your seat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.26,0:14:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆哥与败蜗子秀  开播
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "The Sir Urchin and Snail Fail Show"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  身为铁粉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, as devoted fans
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们必须说服两位偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's our duty to convince our two idols
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重聚复出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get back together
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜剧界的未来寄托于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future of comedy depends on it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先分开才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to split up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才刚躺舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just getting comfy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去找败蜗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go find Snail Fail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你去找海胆哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you track down Sir Urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.98,0:15:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Booyah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出租船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,296)}出租船
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where to, Mac?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我去海胆哥家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me to Sir Urchin's house
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir Urchin?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  海胆哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sir Urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位老是会说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, the guy that goes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Why, you"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's so funny
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是海胆哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Sir Urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir Urchin?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么来开出租船了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you driving a taxi?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我搭档五分钟前闹掰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My partner and I broke up five minutes ago
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.42,0:16:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打那以后  日子便变得难过起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and since then, times have been tough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们之前可搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys were so funny back then
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说  你想不想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, Mac, how would you like
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来当败蜗子二代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be Snail Fail the Second?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would I?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.15,0:16:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would I?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是粉丝送给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probably a gift from one of my adoring fans
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am an adoring fan
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  败蜗子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Snail Fail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to ask
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟海胆哥能不能重聚复出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you and Sir Urchin could get back together again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  为了你们的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, for your adoring fans
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不演低俗喜剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more low comedy for me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我若是想再度踏上舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only way I shall ever step on a stage again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须成为正剧演员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is as a serious dramatic actor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, be gone
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道有家舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know a stage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边的观众会想看你表演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where people would love to see you act
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1368,622)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的鲭鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, poor Mackerel
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认得他  比目鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew him, Halibut
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位爱打趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fellow of infinite jest
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他带领我指引方向上千次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He hath borne me on his fishtail a thousand times
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stink
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许应该叫海胆哥过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should call Sir Urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俺哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What me do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俺哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What me do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么没人笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How come nobody's laughing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的是  俺哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're saying, "What me do?"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是  我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,instead of, "What I do?"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概就这原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good note
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where I go?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, that's not it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.52,0:18:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能有真正可以表演的舞台就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only we had a real stage to perform on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能有真正可以表演的舞台就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I had a real stage to act on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,号外  号外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Extry, extry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478,816)}才艺秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1422,798)}才艺秀
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村才艺大秀今晚开演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big Bikini Bottom Talent Show tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正舞台秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a real stage
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.45,0:18:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等了好久的机会可能要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This might be the break we've been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闻到了重聚的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell a reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,648)}才艺秀
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到裤头村才艺秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Bikini Bottom Talent show
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,456)}裤头村才艺秀
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽情欣赏吧  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it away, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看台下的观众
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all those people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这条是演才艺秀的队伍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this the line for the talent show?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Success
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能看到你们重聚真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's great to see you guys back together again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.20,0:19:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不跟在这位二流子后面上台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not following this riffraff onto the stage
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们先上台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We shall go first
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开  莎士比哑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shove off, Fakespeare
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.47,0:19:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我新搭档派大星才是先来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and my new partner, Patrick, were here first
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那单片眼睛可贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That monocle was priceless
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在变垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有要遭受这般命运的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I do to deserve this fate?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我何曾有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you referring to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原先的演法就很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our act was perfect the way it was
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不应该换掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should never have tried to change it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.97,0:21:06.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,败蜗子  老兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:06.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snail Fail, old buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.02,0:21:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我们的节目里加点严肃表演
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Add some serious acting to our show
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想让我们重聚复出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to get back together again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So do I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我们哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what we do'd
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}一周后
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的鲭鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, poor Mackerel
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认得他  海胆哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew him, Sir Urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位爱打趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fellow of infinite jest
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.01,0:21:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四处探险是他的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nautical nonsense be something he wished
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的笑料何在  老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where be your jokes now, old friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是否还能让我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That I may laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With merriment?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我何有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What hath I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.34,0:22:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们回归了  比以前更搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're back and funnier than ever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.03,0:22:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想花一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We would just like to take a moment
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进行大家所说的公开致意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to give a shout-out, as the kids say
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to our friends
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.49,0:22:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝和派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.09,0:22:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你们  我们绝对没法重聚复出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We couldn't have gotten back together without you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.09,0:22:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
